OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey and damp start with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain moving
OL,7,Fnortheastwards, locally heavy at
OL,8,Ffirst. Gradually turning drier and
OL,9,Fbrighter as the day unfolds. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarm and rather muggy, with low cloud
OL,11,Fhugging some hills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely dry this evening with
OL,14,Fsome spells of brightness. Overnight
OL,15,Fwe will likely see mist and low cloud
OL,16,Fform, with perhaps some spots of
OL,17,Fdrizzle over higher ground. Remaining
OL,18,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
