OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA mostly dry, bright and
OL,6,Fvery warm day across the south of
OL,7,Fregion. Further north will turn
OL,8,Fincreasingly cloudy with some rain
OL,9,Fmoving into Cumbria and perhaps parts
OL,10,Fof Lancashire.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFurther
OL,13,Frain possible on Friday, especially in
OL,14,Fthe north. Becoming drier and brighter
OL,15,Fthis weekend, though still a few
OL,16,Fshowers at first. Warm on Saturday and
OL,17,Fperhaps hot by Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
